# We commit the hpack-generated ocelot.cabal so cabal-only consumers
# (Hackage, plain `cabal build`, IDE tooling) work without running hpack
# first. package.yaml stays the source of truth; do not hand-edit the
# .cabal — let `stack build` regenerate it.

# Haskell build artifacts
*.o
*.hi
*.hie
*.chi
*.chs.h
*.dyn_o
*.dyn_hi
.hspec-failures
.ghc.environment.*

